    Route -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS reencrypt<br/>NetworkPolicy: ingress NS"| KubeRBAC
    CatalogRoute -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS reencrypt<br/>NetworkPolicy: ingress NS"| CatalogProxy

