    RESTApi -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Password<br/>Configurable SSL"| PostgreSQL

    CatalogProxy -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>SubjectAccessReview"| K8sAPI
    CatalogProxy -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>localhost"| CatalogREST
    CatalogREST -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Password"| CatalogDB

    %% Operator flows
    OperatorMgr -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>SA token"| K8sAPI
    K8sAPI -->|"HTTPS/9443<br/>TLS serving cert<br/>API server client cert"| OperatorMgr

    %% External services
    RESTApi -.->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Configurable sslMode"| ExtPG
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS<br/>Bearer Token"| OperatorMgr

